dining experience with beautifully curated courses, premium meats, and exceptional attention to detail. Every dish felt refined, thoughtfully executed, and full of quality.\n\nFrom the presentation to the flavors, everything was elegant and memorable. I genuinely can’t believe I just discovered this hidden gem.\n\nA truly luxurious dining experience worth savoring.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Highly recommended for date nights, anniversaries, celebrations, and special occasions ✨\n\nAn elevated dining experience with beautifully curated courses, premium meats, and exceptional attention to detail. Every dish felt refined, thoughtfully executed, and full of quality.\n\nFrom the presentation to the flavors, everything was elegant and memorable. I genuinely can’t believe I just discovered this hidden gem.\n\nA truly luxurious dining experience worth savoring.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Angelia Jang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111216208011679308278/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKObsyxnyLMmgv71GPS_SJFHEYQjBorrQd9jqVtZ0oPSkFqBdm0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T01:26:53.296229923Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSMVkwcDFiWEZJZEMxclRWaE1jMTlVT0VOdFYwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSMVkwcDFiWEZJZEMxclRWaE1jMTlVT0VOdFYwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7831bb7a8e3:0x9dbf02c72b384d5f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ46i3G4PHwoARX004K8cCv50/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sRWVIQnFaVU5YT1VkSlpGOTNSbm90TTJaR1IzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We came here for the first time yesterday and had the BEST lunch we’ve had in a long time. Food was absolutely fantastic. We got the pork for two and I couldn’t believe how good everything was. This is definitely more traditional Korean BBQ and may be my new favorite in the area. I can’t wait to go back and try to steak but the pork was absolutely amazing. Side dishes as well. And great service. We had our dogs with us on the patio and they gave them treats and just went above and beyond to make sure we had a great meal. Bringing my whole family here soon.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We came here for the first time yesterday and had the BEST lunch we’ve had in a long time. Food was absolutely fantastic. We got the pork for two and I couldn’t believe how good everything was. This is definitely more traditional Korean BBQ and may be my new favorite in the area. I can’t wait to go back and try to steak but the pork was absolutely amazing. Side dishes as well. And great service. We had our dogs with us on the patio and they gave them treats and just went above and beyond to make sure we had a great meal. Bringing my whole family here soon.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Taylor Stanley", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100009459545143984637/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJIik7UInut1kblDE_dHPDjOAD26MxMVjsxFoO9eh0myF2brvw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-21T21:06:51.626017014Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sRWVIQnFaVU5YT1VkSlpGOTNSbm90TTJaR1IzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sRWVIQnFaVU5YT1VkSlpGOTNSbm90TTJaR1IzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7831bb7a8e3:0x9dbf02c72b384d5f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ46i3G4PHwoARX004K8cCv50/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWdk5pMXFUbVJ2ZWtKNGNYUk9TbWR0YjBNek9HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Solid kbbq. Ordered the 65pp beef bbq. Meat quality was above average with them cooking it for you so you can actually talk and enjoy your dinner. Banchan was solid. Nothing that stands out in particular, but definately not lacking in anything. Parking is always a pain in ktown.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Solid kbbq. Ordered the 65pp beef bbq. Meat quality was above average with them cooking it for you so you can actually talk and enjoy your dinner. Banchan was solid. Nothing that stands out in particular, but definately not lacking in anything. Parking is always a pain in ktown.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Dr.Foodie", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104956641486639984498/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1GE-M8D6684yanBhbkjXt1-ZnA-IfL319wrQSRp7VGj8CE0E=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-10T20:34:36.659204889Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWdk5pMXFUbVJ2ZWtKNGNYUk9TbWR0YjBNek9HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWdk5pMXFUbVJ2ZWtKNGNYUk9TbWR0YjBNek9HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7831bb7a8e3:0x9dbf02c72b384d5f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ46i3G4PHwoARX004K8cCv50/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWWVNrWnliREpHYmtjeVNWSTNiMGszWXpVdExVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is my first review, but I’ve been to this place several times already!\nThere’s usually no wait on weekdays, but expect a bit of a line on weekends.\n\nI’ve tried many BBQ restaurants in K-Town, and I can confidently say the meat quality here is the best.\nAll the side dishes are tasty, and the salad is absolutely amazing 🥗\n\nEven if you’re not great at grilling meat, don’t worry the staff is super friendly and helps you out.\nAll my friends are terrible at grilling, so I’m usually the “BBQ master”\nbut here, I finally got to relax 😂\n\nWhen I visited recently, the place was decorated with a fun Halloween vibe it made the atmosphere even better 🎃\nHighly recommend the pork belly — try it with the soy sauce and Korean dipping sauce Perfect combo!\n\nIf you’re looking for authentic Korean BBQ in Los Angeles, this spot in K-Town is a must-visit.\nThe quality, service, and atmosphere easily make it one of my favorite Korean restaurants in LA.\nGreat for food lovers, travelers, or anyone exploring K-Town.\n\n⭐️ Korean BBQ, K-Town Los Angeles, Best Korean Food, Pork Belly, Authentic Korean Restaurant", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is my first review, but I’ve been to this place several times already!\nThere’s usually no wait on weekdays, but expect a bit of a line on weekends.\n\nI’ve tried many BBQ restaurants in K-Town, and I can confidently say the meat quality here is the best.\nAll the side dishes are tasty, and the salad is absolutely amazing 🥗\n\nEven if you’re not great at grilling meat, don’t worry the staff is super friendly and helps you out.\nAll my friends are terrible at grilling, so I’m usually the “BBQ master”\nbut here, I finally got to relax 😂\n\nWhen I visited recently, the place was decorated with a fun Halloween vibe it made the atmosphere even better 🎃\nHighly recommend the pork belly — try it with the soy sauce and Korean dipping sauce Perfect combo!\n\nIf you’re looking for authentic Korean BBQ in Los Angeles, this spot in K-Town is a must-visit.\nThe quality, service, and atmosphere easily make it one of my favorite Korean restaurants in LA.\nGreat for food lovers, travelers, or anyone exploring K-Town.\n\n⭐️ Korean BBQ, K-Town Los Angeles, Best Korean Food, Pork Belly, Authentic Korean Restaurant", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "AJ", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106675166890962112351/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtIi-cOuSHsCiIRiR9BjKnsvEeYdoA7D6byFlAXCqhWqD4lp4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-24T19:26:23.143011028